# ⚡ KEY DESIGN DECISIONS

---

## ✅ 1. Batch Processing

* Runs once daily
* Not real-time

---

## ✅ 2. No Data Deletion

```text
Data accumulates over time
```

---

## ✅ 3. Precomputed Data

* Fast API
* No heavy computation

---

## ✅ 4. Separation of Concerns

* Fetcher → gets data
* Processor → computes
* API → serves

---

